title: The Show Gets Hypnotized + Bobby And Listeners Upset With Raymundo + Caller Needs Advice On ‘Dirty Diaper’ Daycare Situation
itunes:title: The Show Gets Hypnotized + Bobby And Listeners Upset With Raymundo + Caller Needs Advice On ‘Dirty Diaper’ Daycare Situation
description:
Bobby and a bunch of listeners are upset with Raymundo for something he said on the show last week. Sheri Spells stops by and hypnotizes Lunchbox, Morgan2 and Phone Screener Abby. Plus, a listener tells us about her son coming home from the daycare with a dirty diaper...so we all offer her some advice!
